snippet: The Blue Devils came from behind in the second half to beat the Wolfpack for the third time this year, and will face Notre Dame in the quarterfinals of the Atlantic Coast Conference tournament.
abstract: College Basketball Men's Roundup; Duke defeats North Carolina State, 92-89, in second round of Atlantic Coast Conference tournament; other men's scores and news noted.
lead_paragraph: The Blue Devils came from behind in the second half to beat the Wolfpack for the third time this year, and will face Notre Dame in the quarterfinals of the Atlantic Coast Conference tournament.

headline.print_headline: Rally Sends Blue Devils by Wolfpack
headline.main: Rally Sends Blue Devils by Wolfpack
